<SidebarLayout
  title="Our Services – JLG Consulting"
  description="Comprehensive support, from strategy to implementation"
>
  <h1 class="text-center font-heading text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
    Our services to transform your digital projects
  </h1>
  <img
    class="mx-auto w-full my-8 max-w-md dark:brightness-50"
    src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}services.webp`}
    alt="Our services"
  />
  <p class="mb-4">
    At <strong>JLG Consulting</strong>, we support businesses, local authorities, and startups at every stage of their digital projects. Our goal: to help you design, develop, and evolve high-value solutions that are accessible, robust, and tailored to your challenges.
  </p>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2">360° Expertise</h2>
  <p class="mb-4">
    We intervene both upstream and downstream of projects, with a cross-functional approach that combines strategy, design, development, accessibility, and training.
  </p>
  <p>Discover our main services&nbsp;:</p>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
    <li>
      <a href="services/strategic-consulting" class="text-green-700 underline">
        Strategic Consulting
      </a> – To clarify your objectives and lay the foundations for a solid project.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="services/design-ux-ui" class="text-green-700 underline">
        UX/UI Design
      </a> – To design useful, usable, and engaging interfaces.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="services/software-development" class="text-green-700 underline">
        Software Development
      </a> – To build custom, robust, and maintainable solutions.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="services/technical-architecture"
        class="text-green-700 underline"
      >
        Technical Architecture
      </a> – To ensure the scalability, performance, and security of your systems.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="services/accessibility" class="text-green-700 underline">
        Digital Accessibility
      </a> – To make your tools inclusive and compliant with standards.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="services/training" class="text-green-700 underline">
        Training
      </a> – To upskill your teams on key digital topics.
    </li>
  </ul>
</SidebarLayout>